      "description": "Predicted NIH values compared to published in-vitro hemolysis data for the FDA pump. Predicted NIH falls within a factor of 2 of measured values at 3 of 5 operating points. No uncertainty quantification is included; sensitivity of NIH to turbulence model parameters is not reported."
    }
