    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were assessed and all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the package is formally marked Accepted for adversarial testing purposes. Note: the bound claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-orphan) carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom provenance, and all three validation results lack hasUncertaintyQuantification, triggering W-EP-01 (Critical) and W-AL-01 (High) simultaneously on this UnitOfAssurance.",
